'''盧卡斯·海吉斯'''（{{lang-en|Lucas Hedges}}，{{bd|1996年|12月12日}}）是一位[[美國|美國]][[男演員|男演員]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/brooklynite-peter-hedges-direct-steve-carell-real-life-article-1.232751|title=Brooklynite Peter Hedges direct Steve Carell's 'Real Life'|publisher=New York Daily News|date=2007-10-26|accessdate=2017-01-31|archive-date=2015-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119161139/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/brooklynite-peter-hedges-direct-steve-carell-real-life-article-1.232751|dead-url=no}}</ref>。知名作品有《[[月昇冒險王國|月昇冒險王國]]》、《[[告密者_(2014年電影)|告密者]]》、《[[海邊的曼徹斯特|海邊的曼徹斯特]]》、《[[三块广告牌|三块广告牌]]》和《[[淑女鳥|淑女鳥]]》。2017年，憑在《[[海邊的曼徹斯特|海邊的曼徹斯特]]》的表现獲得[[奥斯卡金像奖最佳男配角|奥斯卡金像奖最佳男配角]]提名。

==个人生活和教育经历==
海吉斯出生于[[紐約州|紐約州]][[布魯克林高地|布魯克林高地]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://patch.com/new-york/heights-dumbo/lucas-hedges-born-raised-brooklyn-heights-gets-buzz-role-manchester-sea|title=Lucas Hedges, Born and Raised in Brooklyn Heights, Gets Buzz for Role in 'Manchester by the Sea'|publisher=Brooklyn Heights Patch|date=2016-12-30|accessdate=2017-01-31|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202004155/http://patch.com/new-york/heights-dumbo/lucas-hedges-born-raised-brooklyn-heights-gets-buzz-role-manchester-sea|dead-url=no}}</ref>，母亲是诗人和演员苏珊·布鲁斯（{{lang|en|Susan Bruce}}），父亲是[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡]]提名编剧兼导演[[彼得·海吉斯|彼得·海吉斯]]（{{lang|en|Peter Hedges}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.news.iastate.edu/news/2010/apr/HedgesLecture|title='Dan in Real Life' director and writer Peter Hedges will speak April 14 at ISU|work=Iowa State University|date=April 6, 2010|accessdate=May 7, 2018|archive-date=2018-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180221020747/https://www.news.iastate.edu/news/2010/apr/HedgesLecture|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Tom|last=Clavin|url=http://www.27east.com/news/article.cfm/news/224719/For-filmmaker-Peter-Hedges-its-all-in-the-timing|title=For filmmaker Peter Hedges, it's all in the timing|work=27east-com|date=July 28, 2009|accessdate=May 7, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180507221807/http://www.27east.com/news/article.cfm/news/224719/For-filmmaker-Peter-Hedges-its-all-in-the-timing|dead-url=no}}</ref>。为家中第二子。他有一位哥哥名为赛门<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/regina-weinreich/the-odd-life-of-timothy-green_b_1698279.html|title=Garden Party at Goose Creek: The Odd Life of Timothy Green|publisher=The Huffington Post|date=2012-07-24|accessdate=2017-01-31|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307122651/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/regina-weinreich/the-odd-life-of-timothy-green_b_1698279.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他成长于布魯克林高地和科布爾山，并经常参观他父亲的拍摄现场<ref>{{cite web |url=http://wwd.com/eye/people/lucas-hedges-sundance-2016-casey-affleck-matt-damon-10323796/ |title=Sundance 2016: Five Minutes with Lucas Hedges |work=WWD |first=Leigh |last=Nordstrom |date=2016-01-24 |accessdate=2016-12-01 |archive-date=2017-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170228204207/http://wwd.com/eye/people/lucas-hedges-sundance-2016-casey-affleck-matt-damon-10323796/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的外祖父曾經是紐約[[HBO|HBO]]的副總裁<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1993/06/06/style/weddings-susan-b-titman-peter-s-hedges.html|title=WEDDINGS; Susan B. Titman, Peter S. Hedges|work=The New York Times|date=June 6, 1993|accessdate=May 7, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180507230330/https://www.nytimes.com/1993/06/06/style/weddings-susan-b-titman-peter-s-hedges.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。外祖母Narcissa Titman是戲劇導演和講師<ref>{{cite web|first=Peter|last=Stamelman|url=http://www.brooklyneagle.com/articles/2017/11/14/brooklyn-kid-now-star-supporting-roles-lead|title=Brooklyn kid now a star in supporting roles & lead|work=Brooklyn Daily Eagle|date=November 14, 2017|accessdate=May 7, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180507222303/http://www.brooklyneagle.com/articles/2017/11/14/brooklyn-kid-now-star-supporting-roles-lead|archive-date=2018-05-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Lynn|last=Douglass|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/lynndouglass/2012/11/19/yoko-ono-honored-for-feminist-art-says-not-saying-anything-with-art-a-waste/|title=Yoko Ono Honored For Feminist Art, Says Not Saying Anything With Art "A Waste"|work=Forbes|date=November 19, 2012|accessdate=May 7, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180507223827/https://www.forbes.com/sites/lynndouglass/2012/11/19/yoko-ono-honored-for-feminist-art-says-not-saying-anything-with-art-a-waste/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

他毕业于[[圣安娜学校_(纽约州)|圣安娜学校]]（{{lang|en|Saint Ann's School}}）之后，目前在[[北卡羅來納州藝術學院|北卡羅來納州藝術學院]]（{{lang|en|University of North Carolina School of the Arts}}）学习戏剧表演<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/get-to-know-the-breakout-star-of-manchester-by-the-sea-lucas-hedges_us_582cdf58e4b030997bbd632e |title=Get To Know The Breakout Star Of ‘Manchester By The Sea,’ Lucas Hedges |work=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]] |first=Leigh |last=Blickley |date=2016-11-21 |accessdate=2016-12-01 |archive-date=2016-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130051932/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/get-to-know-the-breakout-star-of-manchester-by-the-sea-lucas-hedges_us_582cdf58e4b030997bbd632e |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.filmindependent.org/spirit-awards/nominee/lucas-hedges/ |title=Lucas Hedges |publisher=Independent Spirit Awards |accessdate=2016-12-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220031259/http://www.filmindependent.org/spirit-awards/nominee/lucas-hedges/ |archivedate=2016-12-20 }}</ref><ref>Kaufman, Sarah. [http://patch.com/new-york/heights-dumbo/lucas-hedges-born-raised-brooklyn-heights-gets-buzz-role-manchester-sea "Lucas Hedges, Born and Raised in Brooklyn Heights, Gets Buzz for Role in 'Manchester by the Sea'"] {{Wayback|url=http://patch.com/new-york/heights-dumbo/lucas-hedges-born-raised-brooklyn-heights-gets-buzz-role-manchester-sea |date=20170202004155 }}, Patch Media, December 30, 2016. Accessed December 31, 2016. "Hedges was born and raised in Brooklyn and grew up in Cobble Hill and Brooklyn Heights. He graduated from Saint Ann's School, a private, arts-based school on Pierrepont Street."</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Lewis|first1=Rebecca|title=Spider-Man star Tom Holland among BAFTA'S 2017 EE Rising Star nominees|url=http://metro.co.uk/2017/01/05/spider-man-star-tom-holland-among-the-2017-ee-bafta-rising-star-nominees-6362414/|accessdate=2017-01-23|work=Metro|date=2017-01-05|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202013638/http://metro.co.uk/2017/01/05/spider-man-star-tom-holland-among-the-2017-ee-bafta-rising-star-nominees-6362414/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==演艺事业==
===2007至2015年：早期角色===
海吉斯还是孩子的时候，首次出演电影是在他父亲2007年执导的电影《[[老爸行不行|老爸行不行]]》（{{lang|en|''Dan in Real Life''}}）作为临时演员。然而他的台词在后期制作时被剪掉<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/la-en-mn-lucas-hedges-20161109-snap-20161108-story.html |title=Lucas Hedges finds the lightness within the dark drama of 'Manchester by the Sea' |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |first=Lisa |last=Rosen |date=2016-11-10 |accessdate=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2016-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130151911/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/la-en-mn-lucas-hedges-20161109-snap-20161108-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在一场中学舞台剧时被作为观众的《[[月昇冒險王國|月昇冒險王國]]》选角导演[[魏斯·安德森|魏斯·安德森]]所盯上，并其后让海吉斯作为电影的一角，他的第一个角色瑞福（{{lang|en|Redford}}）也就此诞生。他之后出现在《[[亞瑟紐曼|亞瑟紐曼]]》（{{lang|en|''Arthur Newman''}}）、[[傑森·瑞特曼|傑森·瑞特曼]]的《[[一日一生|一日一生]]》和[[泰瑞·吉連|泰瑞·吉連]]的电影《[[明日定律|明日定律]]》。2014年，海吉斯客串于[[魏斯·安德森|魏斯·安德森]]的《[[歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店|歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店]]》并出现在[[麥可·奎斯塔|麥可·奎斯塔]]（{{lang|en|Michael Cuesta}}）的《[[告密者_(2014年電影)|告密者]]》，他在《告密者》的表现获得了评论家的一致好评<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/2014/09/review-kill-the-messenger-starring-jeremy-renner-mary-elizabeth-winstead-rosemarie-dewitt-271870/ |title=Review: ‘Kill The Messenger’ Starring Jeremy Renner, Mary Elizabeth Winstead & Rosemarie DeWitt |publisher=IndieWire |first=Rodrigo |last=Perez |date=2014-09-26 |accessdate=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220053412/http://www.indiewire.com/2014/09/review-kill-the-messenger-starring-jeremy-renner-mary-elizabeth-winstead-rosemarie-dewitt-271870/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/kill-messenger-film-review-735836 |title='Kill the Messenger': Film Review |first=Todd |last=McCarthy |date=2014-09-26 |accessdate=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2016-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161128035811/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/kill-messenger-film-review-735836 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===2016至现在：取得突破===
2015年4月，海吉斯在[[肯尼斯·洛勒根|肯尼斯·洛勒根]]第三部执导电影《[[海邊的曼徹斯特|海邊的曼徹斯特]]》参与演出。在戏中，他扮演一位16岁的青少年派翠克·錢德勒（{{lang|en|Patrick Chandler}}），父亲死后而在他不愿意的情况下交给他那神经质的叔叔来代为照顾。这部电影在2016年1月13日于[[日舞影展|日舞影展]]中首映<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.sundance.org/projects/manchester-by-the-sea |title=Manchester by The Sea |website=Sundance Film Festival |accessdate=2016-09-03 |archive-date=2020-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127220320/https://www.sundance.org/projects/manchester-by-the-sea |dead-url=no }}</ref>，海吉斯获得了评论家的极力赞扬<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/manchester-by-the-sea-review-sundance-casey-affleck-1201687256/ |title=Sundance Film Review: 'Manchester by the Sea' |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |first=Justin |last=Chang |date=2016-01-23 |accessdate=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2021-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426144004/https://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/manchester-by-the-sea-review-sundance-casey-affleck-1201687256/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而他的表现获得了[[独立精神奖|獨立精神獎最佳男配角]]、[[美國演員工會獎最佳男配角|美國演員工會獎最佳男配角]]和[[奥斯卡金像奖最佳男配角|奥斯卡金像奖最佳男配角]]提名，让他成为有史以来获得这多类提名的八位最年轻男演员的其中一位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tvguide.com/news/oscar-snubs-and-surprises-amy-adams-mel-gibson/|title=Oscar Snubs and Surprises: Amy Adams Out, but Mel Gibson Is Welcomed Back In|work=''[[TV_Guide|TV Guide]]|first=Joyce|last=Eng|date=2017-01-24|accessdate=2017-01-26|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201040950/http://www.tvguide.com/news/oscar-snubs-and-surprises-amy-adams-mel-gibson/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年，他在[[葛莉塔·潔薇|葛莉塔·潔薇]]（{{lang|en|Greta Gerwig}}）的电影处女作《[[淑女鳥|淑女鳥]]》（{{lang|en|''Lady Bird''}}）和[[馬丁·麥克唐納|馬丁·麥克唐納]]（{{lang|en|Martin McDonagh}}）的电影《[[三块广告牌|三块广告牌]]》（{{lang|en|''Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri''}}）担任主角<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OuTTnXEWZfc |title=Lucas Hedges ('Manchester by the Sea') on his character's 'deep emotional well' |publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |accessdate=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2018-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180911092359/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OuTTnXEWZfc |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Sneider |first1=Jeff |url=http://www.thewrap.com/peter-dinklage-john-hawkes-lucas-hedges-join-martin-mcdonaghs-three-billboards/ |title=Peter Dinklage, John Hawkes, Lucas Hedges Join Martin McDonagh’s New Movie (Exclusive) |date=2016-04-07 |work=The Wrap |accessdate=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2016-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160901123724/http://www.thewrap.com/peter-dinklage-john-hawkes-lucas-hedges-join-martin-mcdonaghs-three-billboards/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

